sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Watch as Apple Watch
    participant Speech as SpeechService
    participant NLP as SocialGraphEngine
    participant App as AppModel
    participant API as FastAPI /api/signals

    User->>Watch: Tap complication or say wake phrase
    Watch->>App: WatchConnectivity start capture
    User->>Speech: "hey it's nice to meet you"
    Speech->>Speech: AVAudioEngine + SFSpeechRecognizer
    Speech-->>App: Live transcript chunks
    App->>NLP: process transcript
    NLP-->>App: PersonNode name org role interests icpScore
    App->>App: sessionLog.record + syncWatchState
    App->>API: POST CapturedSignal JSON
    API-->>App: 202 connection_id warmth routing gmail_draft
    App-->>User: ConnectionsView updates
